sequenceDiagram
    actor U as You (in Claude)
    participant M as jetder-mcp
    participant J as Jetder API
    participant C as Cloudflare DNS
    U->>M: domain-create (domain)
    M->>J: domain.create
    J-->>M: ok
    U->>M: domain-get
    M->>J: read DNS records
    J-->>M: pointTo (A/CNAME) + ownership/SSL TXT
    U->>M: cf-dns-create (records)
    Note over M,C: pointTo proxied=true gives instant Cloudflare SSL, TXT stays DNS-only
    M->>C: create DNS records
    C-->>M: ok
    U->>M: route-create-v2 (domain, target deployment://name)
    M->>J: route.createV2
    J-->>M: routed
    M-->>U: live (HTTPS) at https://your-domain
